{"tid":858734,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解神設計人既食道同氣管交錯咁on9?","createTime":"2018-10-12T04:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T13:18:22.000Z","uid":52817,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7ba731ae81f6184d9a0f5563d5d550d0a4670b","tid":858734,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"係咪方便佢睇你唔順眼果陣，點都可以整死你－唔食野就餓死，食野就哽死??<br />\n<br />\n有冇支持創造論／智慧設計論既巴打可以解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8129148439958d23736b52b443bbb5d0768b727d","tid":858734,"uid":70538,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T04:24:11.000Z","msg":"因為佢自己都係咁on9"},{"pid":"69663119acbb1dcbacab5196b53a01d1e7b6d9c0","tid":858734,"uid":196484,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:05:36.000Z","msg":"方便呑精"},{"pid":"8c2228086e9852f070d312c6c44b9507ac34da73","tid":858734,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"因係身體冇咁多位比你擺多條管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe6060b1fd3330770fd6b1fe8ceb2045f7b7102","tid":858734,"uid":105678,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:48:20.000Z","msg":"調番轉咁諗，你鼻塞嘅時候都可以用口呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ddb875655c1b7971a6157e957a699dfd4c73995","tid":858734,"uid":147710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"因為我們嘅祖先條氣管同食道係共用一條管道，個陣祖先都住係海入面。<br />\n自此以後，我們所有係水入面嘅嘅祖先都採取差唔多嘅呼吸同進食策略：等啲水從個口到入黎，想食野嘅時候，就關左通往呼吸器官（鰓裂）嘅閘門，打開通往消化嘅閥門，就食到水入面嘅食物；等到想呼吸個陣，就關消化道嘅閥門，打開呼吸道嘅閥門。<br />\n利申：鳩up"},{"pid":"9894d2867e1646040c452e41766e7573908d695c","tid":858734,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ddb875655c1b7971a6157e957a699dfd4c73995","tid":858734,"uid":147710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"因為我們嘅祖先條氣管同食道係共用一條管道，個陣祖先都住係海